<td>"How the New Interest Rate Hike Affects Your Mortgage"</td>
<td>High</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<p>Use the primary search query in the headline. Place it near the front. Keep headlines under 70 characters so they display fully in Top Stories and search results.</p>
